name: Around Eleven
description:
#2 AROUND ELEVEN - Mersaterrestre Series

It's summer and there;s a lot of people around.
The clock strikes the 11.11: make a wish.
A castle in the rock, a trip around.
The antique echoes repits: “le dije: mami entonces vamono ahora que pasan las horas”

Mersaterrestre it's a collection of icons, landscapes, symbols that doesn't exist. But maybe they do.
